---
// Host/VM + Tailscale network diagram for the NixOS homelab post.
---

<figure class="not-prose my-8 flex flex-col items-center">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
    <span
      class="border-border bg-background text-muted-foreground rounded-full border px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium tracking-wide uppercase"
    >
      Tailscale tailnet
    </span>
    <div class="border-border h-4 border-l border-dashed"></div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="border-border bg-muted/40 relative w-full max-w-md rounded-xl border p-5 pt-8"
  >
    <div class="absolute -top-3 left-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span
        class="bg-background text-muted-foreground px-2 text-xs font-medium tracking-wide uppercase"
      >
        Host — Manjaro
      </span>
      <span
        class="bg-background text-muted-foreground border-border rounded-full border px-2 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-medium"
      >
        tailscale
      </span>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
      <div class="border-border h-4 border-l border-dashed"></div>

      <div
        class="border-accent/40 bg-background relative w-full rounded-lg border p-4 pt-7"
      >
        <div class="absolute -top-3 left-4 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span
            class="bg-background text-accent px-2 text-xs font-medium tracking-wide uppercase"
          >
            VM — NixOS
          </span>
          <span
            class="bg-background text-accent border-accent/40 rounded-full border px-2 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-medium"
          >
            tailscale
          </span>
        </div>

        <ul class="text-foreground grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm">
          <li class="border-border rounded-md border px-2 py-1.5 text-center">
            Immich
          </li>
          <li class="border-border rounded-md border px-2 py-1.5 text-center">
            Caddy
          </li>
          <li class="border-border rounded-md border px-2 py-1.5 text-center">
            Postgres
          </li>
          <li class="border-border rounded-md border px-2 py-1.5 text-center">
            oauth2-proxy
          </li>
          <li
            class="border-border col-span-2 rounded-md border px-2 py-1.5 text-center"
          >
            oci-containers (omniroute, mboard, camofox, …)
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-muted-foreground mt-3 flex justify-center text-xs">
      <span class="border-border bg-background rounded-full border px-3 py-1">
        virtiofs ↔ shared photo library
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <figcaption class="text-muted-foreground mt-3 text-center text-sm">
    Host and VM both join the same tailnet — everything else declarative
    lives inside the NixOS VM, with virtiofs bridging the bits that need to
    stay on disk.
  </figcaption>
</figure>
